{"id":8259,"date":"2026-03-18T17:15:44","date_gmt":"2026-03-18T10:15:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8259"},"modified":"2026-03-18T17:15:44","modified_gmt":"2026-03-18T10:15:44","slug":"neo-heliopan-e1000-mang-loc-uvb-diu-nhe-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/neo-heliopan-e1000-mang-loc-uvb-diu-nhe-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Neo Heliopan E1000 \u2013 M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc UVB d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu Octinoxate t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u201cng\u00f4i sao\u201d ch\u1ed1ng tia UVB truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, th\u00ec Neo Heliopan E1000 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi \u2013 v\u1eabn b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u01b0ng d\u1ecbu h\u01a1n v\u1edbi da. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 organic \u01b0u \u00e1i v\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t, \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n sinh h\u1ecdc cao.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-neo-heliopan-e1000\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Neo Heliopan E1000<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8999 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-2-1.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ed5 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Neo Heliopan E1000\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-2-1.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-2-1-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-2-1-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-2-1-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc\/INCI: Isoamyl p-Methoxycinnamate<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i: Neo Heliopan E1000 (Symrise, \u0110\u1ee9c)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u00f3m: M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 tia UVB<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ed5 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5: 280\u2013320 nm, \u0111\u1ec9nh kho\u1ea3ng 310 nm, ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng DNA do UVB<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c: T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1eeb r\u01b0\u1ee3u isoamyl chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean (th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb m\u00eda \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea7u d\u1eeba), n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n sinh h\u1ecdc (biodegradable).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ph\u00e1p l\u00fd: \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i EU, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00dac; ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FDA Hoa K\u1ef3 ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn trong danh m\u1ee5c ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-hoat-chat-neo-heliopan-e1000\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t Neo Heliopan E1000<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Neo Heliopan E1000 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tia UVB \u2013 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh g\u00e2y b\u1ecfng n\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng DNA b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t. So v\u1edbi Octinoxate (Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate), ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y \u00edt g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, b\u1ec1n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 kh\u1ecfi ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng, r\u00e1m \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 s\u1edbm do UVB.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch cao v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng silicone.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y tr\u1eafng m\u1eb7t, kh\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng d\u1ea7u, t\u1ea1o b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu khi d\u00f9ng l\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8264 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-3.webp\" alt=\"Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t Neo Heliopan\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c, Isoamyl p-Methoxycinnamate h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb tia UVB v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7t nh\u1eb9, ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n tia n\u00e0y xuy\u00ean qua bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8265\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8265\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8265 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-4.webp\" alt=\"C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Neo Heliopan E1000\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Neo-Heliopan-E1000-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8265\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Neo Heliopan E1000<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac cinnamate nh\u01b0ng thay th\u1ebf nh\u00f3m r\u01b0\u1ee3u b\u1eb1ng isoamyl, gi\u00fap t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh quang h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u00e2n r\u00e3 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ch\u1ee9a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y gi\u1eef hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 SPF \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n sau nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1edd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-va-phoi-hop-pho-bien\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Neo Heliopan E1000 tan t\u1ed1t trong d\u1ea7u, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng d\u1ea1ng s\u1eefa, lotion, fluid, oil-free ho\u1eb7c hybrid.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t ph\u1ed5 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, n\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tinosorb S (Bis-Ethylhexyloxyphenol Methoxyphenyl Triazine): m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng ph\u1ed5 UVA\u2013UVB v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Uvinul A Plus (Diethylamino Hydroxybenzoyl Hexyl Benzoate): t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 UVA1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Uvinul T 150 (Ethylhexyl Triazone): t\u0103ng SPF m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Zinc Oxide ho\u1eb7c Titanium Dioxide: gi\u00fap ch\u1ed1ng UVA2, gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-chong-nang-pho-rong-mela-gsc\/\">Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng Mela<\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-su-dung-neo-heliopan-e1000\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Neo Heliopan E1000\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-kem-chong-nang-co-neo-heliopan-e1000-dung-tot-nhat-khi-nao\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 Neo Heliopan E1000 d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi n\u00e0o?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ch\u1ee9a Neo Heliopan E1000 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c da kh\u00f4 c\u1ea7n n\u1ec1n d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, \u00edt c\u1ed3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng da ban ng\u00e0y, make-up ho\u1eb7c CC cream ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00f4 r\u00e1o, n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111i bi\u1ec3n hay ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng khi \u0111i bi\u1ec3n v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc, c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u1ec3n (t\u1ea9y san h\u00f4 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9c sinh sinh v\u1eadt bi\u1ec3n). Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 khu v\u1ef1c bi\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chong-chi-dinh-hoac-han-che\"><\/span><b>Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u1eb7c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u01b0a ghi nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1eb7c hi\u1ec7u, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u00ean test v\u00f9ng nh\u1ecf n\u1ebfu da \u0111ang vi\u00eam ho\u1eb7c nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m cao.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc n\u00e0y \u0111\u01a1n l\u1ebb v\u00ec n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac n\u1eafng m\u1ea1nh; c\u1ea7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc UVA \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n ph\u1ed5.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 da d\u1ea7u d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u00eam ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu (Centella, Allantoin, Niacinamide) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phu-nu-co-thai-va-cho-con-bu-co-dung-duoc-khong\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9c t\u00ednh n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft hay \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn thai nhi. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u1eabn n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng kho\u00e1ng (Zinc Oxide, Titanium Dioxide) n\u1ebfu da r\u1ea5t nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 b\u1ec7nh da n\u1ec1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n tham kh\u1ea3o:<\/p>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">Ataman Chemicals. (n.d.). <em>Neo Heliopan E1000 (Isoamyl p-Methoxycinnamate)<\/em>. <a class=\"underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current\/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current\" href=\"https:\/\/www.atamanchemicals.com\/neo-heliopan-e1000_u30601\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/www.atamanchemicals.com\/neo-heliopan-e1000_u30601\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">European Chemicals Agency. (n.d.). <em>Isoamyl p-Methoxycinnamate: Substance information<\/em>. ECHA. <a class=\"underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current\/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current\" href=\"https:\/\/echa.europa.eu\/substance-information\/-\/substanceinfo\/100.068.849\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/echa.europa.eu\/substance-information\/-\/substanceinfo\/100.068.849<\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">INCIDecoder. (n.d.). <em>Isoamyl p-Methoxycinnamate<\/em>. <a class=\"underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current\/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current\" href=\"https:\/\/incidecoder.com\/ingredients\/isoamyl-p-methoxycinnamate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/incidecoder.com\/ingredients\/isoamyl-p-methoxycinnamate<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Skinterest. (2023, February 21). <em>Reef safety: Crisis or con?<\/em> <a class=\"underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current\/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current\" href=\"https:\/\/skinterest.com.au\/2023\/02\/21\/reef-safety-crisis-or-con\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/skinterest.com.au\/2023\/02\/21\/reef-safety-crisis-or-con\/<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00a0Isoamyl p-Methoxycinnamate (Neo Heliopan E1000) \u2013 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc UVB th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n da, b\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.\u00a0<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8998,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8259","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8259","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8259"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8259\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9289,"href":"http